{"tid":630873,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"［軸心國］俄譴責聯軍行動 僅三票支持","createTime":"2018-04-16T03:47:30.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-16T10:30:34.000Z","uid":38671,"like":10,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"0a3753e6b68d7264acd50ee024a3933408dd27c1","tid":630873,"uid":38671,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-16T03:47:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n俄羅斯周六在聯合國安理會召集緊急會議，試圖推動安理會通過決議，譴責聯軍對敘利亞的攻擊。<br />\n<br />\n但是，俄羅斯的決議草案僅獲得安理會15個成員國中的三票支持，因此被否決。除了俄羅斯自己，僅有中國和玻利維亞投了贊成票。<br />\n<br />\n除了在聯合國緊跟俄羅斯，中國政府還通過官方媒體批評美英法的軍事行動。<br />\n<br />\n中共黨報《人民日報》周日發表評論文章，批評西方的&quot;任性軍事干預害處多多&quot;。<br />\n<br />\n《人民日報》子報《環球時報》則發表社評說，&quot;美英法對敘實施任性攻擊是可恥的&quot;。<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.bbc.com/zhongwen/trad/world-43778620\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.com%2Fzhongwen%2Ftrad%2Fworld-43778620&d=Ls1nbJgqs3x2s7Xao1cZqbIOlR6kLHi1VdsYCD5DrTY%3D&h=d3f7124a\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.com%2Fzhongwen%2Ftrad%2Fworld-43778620&h=4a8c3588\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.bbc.com/zhongwen/trad/world-43778620</a>"},{"pid":"3303bb8f1e2bf84dcdcf9b5b16a62aa9a88782c6","tid":630873,"uid":35815,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-16T03:48:58.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"6371cec008db9cc5c84e19bc7e11bedfb8f33cc9","tid":630873,"uid":126305,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-16T08:24:13.000Z","msg":"夠膽出聲咩"},{"pid":"b2f1c3b5ce6d214dda67d5b3f95f314362e458ed","tid":630873,"uid":39277,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-16T08:26:09.000Z","msg":"玻利維亞咩料<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/02.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b71500d90604c2e366cbea745ce879613400c753","tid":630873,"uid":41205,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1